{"tid":1883502,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馬國明居住屋苑爆肺炎","createTime":"2020-02-17T04:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T10:21:20.000Z","uid":49267,"like":457,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce816793c1415f6d542f728ac3a5bd49192945a","tid":1883502,"uid":49267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T04:05:17.000Z","msg":"馬國明居住屋苑爆肺炎<br />\n<br />\n今年剛奪視帝的馬國明與家人同住在太古城，昨日位於太古城明宮閣一名54歲男住戶確診感染武漢肺炎，患者沒有外遊紀錄，截至昨日傍晚6時，患者對病毒初步呈陽性反應，目前在東區醫院隔離並接受治療，消息傳出後，同區居民人人自危。馬國明昨日回覆傳媒時表示，不擔心受到感染，並指自己與患者不是住在同一座，他說：「其實唔近我嗰度，唔使擔心，我會做足個人清潔，勤洗手、戴口罩就冇問題。」<br />\n<br />\n馬國明上周四在情人節前夕踏入46歲生日，近日都無懼疫情，頻頻與好友飯敍慶祝，不少網民催促單身的馬國明快些拍拖。"},{"pid":"191af617bf2223295b40439548d09a7ef4b6cf80","tid":1883502,"uid":293648,"like":83,"dislike":3,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T04:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass